public
string
add_history
string $message;,integer $err_level;[,boolean $debug_backtrace_provide_object=false]
This methode lets you to add custom histories into the Template historic.
$err_level can be :
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;256 => 'E_USER_ERROR'
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;512 => 'E_USER_WARNING'
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1024 => 'E_USER_NOTICE'
$debug_backtrace_provide_object specifies if you want to store data about object in use when you add your history entry.
